CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW SSOVPERMROL AS SELECT a.APLICACION as APLICACION,a.IDXAPLICACION as IDXAPLICACION,aa.ICONO as ICONO,aa.IDXSSOMENU as IDXSSOMENU,aa.MENU as MENU,ab.IDXSSOMENUITEM as IDXSSOMENUITEM,ab.ITEM as ITEM,ab.NAMESPACE as NAMESPACE,ab.PAGE as PAGE,ab.URL as URL,ac.ROL as ROL,ac.DASHBOARD as DASHBOARD FROM SSOMENUITEM ab
 INNER JOIN 
SSOMENU aa ON aa.IDXSSOMENU = ab.IDSSOMENU0 INNER JOIN 
SSOROLESMENU ad ON ad.IDSSOMENUITEM0 = ab.IDXSSOMENUITEM INNER JOIN 
SSOROL ac ON ac.IDXSSOROL = ad.IDSSOROL0 INNER JOIN 
SSOAPLICACION a ON a.IDXAPLICACION = aa.IDSSOAPLICACION0;
